
This project offeres reusable code for socket connection in c++11.
The content consists of 

"SocketBase" class -> This is a base class with reusable code of socket connection required in building both server and client.

"SocketAccept" class -> This is a derived class out of "SocketBase" class to create server. start() function in this class run a server's bind, listen and accept functionalities.   

"SocketConnect" class -> This is a derived class out of "SocketBase" class to create client. start() function in this class connects the client to the server.
